# Copy to .env and fill in when starting v2 (Alpaca paper trading).
# Paper and live use separate key pairs -- never mix them.
#
# The Symbols tab's live/delayed quotes (engine/quotes.py) also read these.
# Market data is the same API for paper and live, so EITHER pair works for
# quotes -- the code prefers ALPACA_API_KEY, then falls back to the paper
# pair. Free-tier data is the delayed IEX feed, which is all the watchlist
# needs. Restart the API after editing this file so the keys are picked up.
ALPACA_API_KEY=
ALPACA_SECRET_KEY=
ALPACA_PAPER_API_KEY=
ALPACA_PAPER_SECRET_KEY=
